title: Upgrading from Pixel to Pixel 5 - which SIM card?
content: When I received my Pixel 5 phone (which shipped with a SIM card already in it), I removed the SIM card from my old pixel and put it in the new Pixel 5. My network is Google Fi. Should I have used the SIM card that shipped with the Pixel 5 instead in order to get 5G service?
